    <br>
    <p>What makes pickleball special isn’t just the rules or the paddle—it’s the vibe. Games move
        quickly, rallies stay interesting, and skill gaps matter less than you’d expect. You can play
        a competitive match or just show up for a few casual games and still have a great time. It’s a
        sport where improvement sneaks up on you, often disguised as fun.</p>
